%% Request tenant resolution. See 08-background-and-storage-isolation.md
flowchart TB
  Req[request] --> Proxy[proxy.ts strips x-tenant-id header]
  Proxy --> Kind{entry point}
  Kind -- admin/portal --> Sess[getPrincipal - signed cookie ONLY]
  Sess --> TidS[principal.tenantId]
  Kind -- cron/webhook --> Bg[resolveBackgroundTenant]
  Bg --> TidB[explicit tenant or reference tenant]
  TidS --> Run[runWithTenant -> AsyncLocalStorage]
  TidB --> Run
  Run --> Handler[handler + redis chokepoint use ctx tenant]
  Sess -. forged header .-> Ignored[header ignored - not authoritative]
